DatasourceRoutes --> TasksDocuments : index documents
AgentRegistryRoutes --> BackendRegistryService : register/list
DbRoutes --> QdrantDatabaseManager : db introspection
McpRoutes --> TasksMCP : MCP requests
SystemRoutes --> TasksDB : health/status

%% Runtime + orchestrator
